    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "59dc08ed623035dc220068fa"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "The word is that the JumpShip returned and is currently orbiting [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGaul],Gaul]] and hiring mercenaries to search for the missing expedition. \n\nSo, since we are desperate for contracts, to me this might be the lucky break we were looking for.",
      "branches": [
