    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ccd949cb28e0a821ad830db"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "OK, not her then, but what about pirates though? It's not the first time that someone fakes a distress signal in order to ambush the rescue party. \n\nLike you said Darius, this is the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeriphery],Periphery]] and it has its own set of rules. Just saying that we better be prepared for what might be out there. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
